This idea is extended to the interaction of ethylene on Pt single crystal surfaces. The adsorption of ethylene as π-bonded state has been reported on (2×1) Pt(1 1 0) and Pt(2 1 0) surfaces, which are very highly stepped
[25]
,
[26]
